item.title: CVE-2023-23630|2024-08-02T10:35:33.606Z -- eta-dev -- eta
item.description: Eta is an embedded JS templating engine that works inside Node, Deno, and the browser. XSS attack - anyone using the Express API is impacted. The problem has been resolved. Users should upgrade to version 2.0.0. As a workaround, don't pass user supplied things directly to `res.render`.
